<ab facs="#facs_300_r1l22"><expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Weͣr <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ ſıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der wır mechtıg <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> . darynn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_300_r1l23">ıcht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>handelten</expan> oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teten denn ſıe pılleıch <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> . mugt Jr </ab>
