<ab facs="#facs_300_r1l25">tun <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> . was vns darcʒu ʒutun gebüret ſo wır das erfüren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_300_r1l26">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb . <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_300_r1l27"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
